$ govctl work new Test Task
Created work item: gov/work/<DATE>-test-task.toml
  ID: WI-<DATE>-001
exit: 0

$ govctl work add WI-<DATE>-001 journal First progress update
Added 'First progress update' to WI-<DATE>-001.journal
exit: 0

$ govctl work add WI-<DATE>-001 journal Second progress update
Added 'Second progress update' to WI-<DATE>-001.journal
exit: 0

$ govctl work show WI-<DATE>-001
